{"tid":193710,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"德X學車中伏經歷","createTime":"2017-04-09T13:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T02:22:36.000Z","uid":75132,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b009bfb1ef8350ac4fc54c020ae4372df4ba7d1b","tid":193710,"uid":75132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"我跟過2個師傅<br />\n第1個師傅 成82歲 成日係到hea我<br />\n問佢野又唔教 又係到灑我時間<br />\n成日停架車係到 係到廢up up親最少3個字<br />\n成日講埋灑D唔關事學車既野<br />\n而第2個師傅 教左我一堂 <br />\n佢就話有D事唔係香港 <br />\n要等2星期到先教到我<br />\n咁我過左2星期再打比佢<br />\n點知佢就同我講<br />\n教我唔到 叫我轉第2個師傅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教我唔到又唔一早同我講<br />\n灑左成2個星期先同我講<br />\n我仲有唔夠3個星期就考 <br />\n好似咩都冇學過咁 <br />\n應該點做好<br />\n已準備510 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ecc2c07188453bd24277fd969ffce5b97a174c","tid":193710,"uid":75132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:17:44.000Z","msg":"假如想學車 <br />\n去呢間既話小心中伏"},{"pid":"5340ad6d01b48101835f410d7c885def5d5122f2","tid":193710,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:48:46.000Z","msg":"82歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會教教下瓜柴,要你去落口供"},{"pid":"8502b0ec46bff91904fc7aed1a9401e6965484ee","tid":193710,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:00:20.000Z","msg":"咁嘅節奏 碌柒啦你"},{"pid":"d10bc8e439ccd915970a3b30ade5674df6885811","tid":193710,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:05:08.000Z","msg":"82歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa364d94b94f92e3dbdc76c938b7e28624b5d34","tid":193710,"uid":84116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"28歲下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3239926b1a5c9421eeb7e555966d3d631973b7","tid":193710,"uid":75132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82721d3bc209f848fe4274c9ead01ec38589b095","tid":193710,"uid":34878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:11:18.000Z","msg":"唔撚係姓伍㗎"},{"pid":"6f46ec92047e4323064e69de68ff88829ec74fd1","tid":193710,"uid":75132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔撚係姓伍㗎</blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"d658d4164aa843036f5e4c9c97f4beeaaf48aa69","tid":193710,"uid":75132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔撚係姓伍㗎</blockquote><br />\n你都有跟佢學?"},{"pid":"6d9778b11a62b521dd0200f651dae0fc175ff4ff","tid":193710,"uid":34878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:13:25.000Z","msg":"呢個仆街嚟㗎&hellip;中撚過伏&hellip;寸下佢就嬲&hellip;垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bf8c1379312cd4dbdbe7f0c8e59ea7614c1b11","tid":193710,"uid":34878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"成日講佢有個二奶幫佢生左個仔"},{"pid":"90682ee22502efea747d221ddd413753acea26fa","tid":193710,"uid":86438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:16:57.000Z","msg":