lass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀"},{"pid":"4c7cfb4f602f405fd78034828998fe7923a0b56e","tid":193710,"uid":75132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出面搵師傅好過啦</blockquote><br />\n我呢家打算搵出邊師傅學<br />\n4月28考"},{"pid":"04cdd1c01d6b1e51f0750cbd361622efbc933d8a","tid":193710,"uid":75132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出面搵師傅好過啦</blockquote><br />\n我呢家打算搵出邊師傅學<br />\n4月28考</blockquote><br />\n我驚唔夠時間"},{"pid":"8f63da0aa52924cd33a965993305e6c783dfa637","tid":193710,"uid":88306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:32:38.000Z","msg":"打去德安投訴，佢會轉出面師傅比你。"},{"pid":"57f16871e692e7cbf70a1d40b8a5168e7b1a7ec1","tid":193710,"uid":75132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:42:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打去德安投訴，佢會轉出面師傅比你。</blockquote><br />\n我聽日會打去 <br />\n希望快D比到師傅我學啦"},{"pid":"d29df6aad959e2cbfd7a829e9e1fc8f17805db64","tid":193710,"uid":86438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪混波私家車？</blockquote><br />\n棍VAN</blockquote><br />\n個陣我又係學呢間 棍私家車<br />\n<br />\n有個阿伯教 都唔係教得好 都算<br />\n<br />\n到我考試個陣，考泊車，一踩架車就失控 勁快 差d撞<br />\n<br />\n我當時已知賴野 平時係我學車個陣個阿伯根本踩住個break，搞到我唔知比幾多力"},{"pid":"5247e38045f457d3e55df9be58dee2853aefe31a","tid":193710,"uid":29000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打去德安投訴，佢會轉出面師傅比你。</blockquote><br />\n我聽日會打去 <br />\n希望快D比到師傅我學啦</blockquote><br />\n去九龍塘行一轉問下都有師傅喇，跟街師傅好過搵學堂<br />\n利申：聽日考 學左十二堂"},{"pid":"8d7481db8d83b16698877d440793b155a94d110b","tid":193710,"uid":88306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:38:47.000Z","msg":"之前我屌9個幫我踏住break 既師傅。<br />\n叫我行快d 但又幫我踏break ,我最後屌9佢再踏大油門。"},{"pid":"b3c91701042d2b561dc83bd21deb74bf641c4122","tid":193710,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔撚係姓伍㗎</blockquote><br />\n你都有跟佢學?</blockquote><br />\n3年前我都係伍師傅學生，油塘<br />\n幾好既佢 不過初初學真係會要你停埋一邊講道理 好長氣"},{"pid":"aba0eb6bc77ca645a93fd187c7cbe51d030ace56","tid":193710,"uid":75132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔撚係姓伍㗎</blockquote><br />\n你都有跟佢學?</blockquote><br />\n3年前我都係伍師傅學生，油塘<br />\n幾好既佢 不過初初學真係會要你停埋一邊講道理 好長氣</blockquote><br />\n佢最煩停埋一邊講道理 好長氣 <br />\n一講最少成3個鐘<br />\n同埋成日講D唔關學車既野"},{"pid":"df9b435d886a74230a78efcecfe78f907cfc5e3a","tid":193710,"uid":20443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:12:34.000Z","msg":"咁趕應該冇咩街師傅有期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55271a36594a5ec3a48b82c088ef9cb07bdc03a","tid":193710,"uid":75132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:45:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁趕應該冇咩街師傅有期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多得條仆街 <br />\n又話教到我 <br />\n等左2個星期又話唔教"},{"pid":"460021cb89845bbdf491f2035e47230af6fb7052","tid":193710,"uid":29000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:52:35.000Z","msg":"3星期夠哂啦日日學既話"},{"pid":"e38a8ab99cdaac5ab51270150533582b6448a55e","tid":193710,"uid":29000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:56:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁趕應該冇咩街師傅有期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多得條仆街 <br />\n又話教到我 <br />\n等左2個星期又話唔教</blockquote><br />\n一係排過喇，一係就快手搵師傅教，試下去九龍塘問下，好多人任問"},{"pid":"41901b24f8c9dc8b7dfa80f30cda2d31bfeb7578","tid":193710,"uid":75132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3星期夠哂啦日日學既話</blockquote><br />\n好彩我呢家日日都可以學到"},{"pid":"e4872df52768f24cff3f0419272214e8ccac9f2d","tid":193710,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike